  25:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****                ##### I2C peripheral Extended features  #####
  26:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  27:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c **** 
  28:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   [..] Comparing to other previous devices, the I2C interface for STM32N6xx
  29:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        devices contains the following additional features
  30:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c **** 
  31:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Possibility to disable or enable Analog Noise Filter
  32:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Use of a configured Digital Noise Filter
  33:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Disable or enable wakeup from Stop mode(s)
  34:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Disable or enable Fast Mode Plus
  35:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c **** 
  36:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****                      ##### How to use this driver #####
  37:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  38:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   [..] This driver provides functions to configure Noise Filter and Wake Up Feature
  39:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure I2C Analog noise filter using the function HAL_I2CEx_ConfigAnalogFilter()
  40:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure I2C Digital noise filter using the function HAL_I2CEx_ConfigDigitalFilter()
  41:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure the enable or disable of I2C Wake Up Mode using the functions :
  42:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_EnableWakeUp()
  43:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_DisableWakeUp()
  44:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure the enable or disable of fast mode plus driving capability using the functions :
  45:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_ConfigFastModePlus()
  46:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   @endverbatim
  47:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   */
